name: Terminal LLM Chatbot for PDFs
description: Uses local LLAMA 2, pdf data extraction techniques, and Retrieval-Augmented Generation to let the user talk to a LLM about a specified PDF within the terminal, allowing the user to ask questions to the LLM and providing the LLM with snippets of the PDF based on an FAISS similarity search.

name: Cancer Classifying CNN
description: Uses simple Keras models and architectures to train and validate a CNN on three types of breast cancer cells; MCF-7, MCF-10A, MDA-MB-231.

name: Stock Price Predicting LSTM
description: Uses Sequential LSTM model to predict close price of TSLA stock based on past years' close price history.

name: GAN Clothing Generator
description: Uses a Keras clothing dataset to develop a GAN to generate similar images.

name: Mandelbrot Set Visualizer
description: Uses a C++ graphics library SFML to generate a plot of the mandelbrot set at any arbitrary position and magnification of the fractal.

name: League of Legends Skillshot Dodge Simulator
description: Uses a C++ graphics library SFML to draw a player and projectiles, detects keyboard and mouse activity to let the player warm up their mechanics by dodging skillshots and aiming at moving enemies.

name: Attack on Titan Video Game in Java
description: Project for CPSC 210 at UBC. Custom program that detects collision for various collidable objects within a grid, optimizing the amount of collision checks, and uses OOP design principles learned within the course to a full extent.
